      public static String generateEdgeID(Node startNode, Node endNode) throws EdgeToSelfException
      Used to generate a non-unique edge ID between two nodes (non-unique as its the same output for switched inputs). Its static because it needs to be called in the edge manager class to calculate edge IDs efficiently.
      Parameters:
